title: ring of sudden impact
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A creature wearing this ring can activate it right before they suffer blunt force trauma. The wearer becomes immune to bludgeoning-type damage for 6 seconds. Once this feature has been used, it cannot be used again for 7 days.